replies.body:
Honestly the TP change was to prevent TP Ganks without any warning. I think in general if they wanna shorten the cooldown and keep the visibility changes, they'd have a balanced TP. The whole no vision while they're TP'ing in and "HolyshitwheredidIrelia....and I'm dead" was stupid and all. On the flipside, if you place deep wards and your enemy support is not clearing them and forgets about them, then you kinda deserve to get dove upon from that ward you didn't clear. It's just a thought. Clear the wards if you can, it will save you from TP ganks from behind.

Cause everyone knows getting a Wuju blade or a set of Irelia's knives or even a giant monkey's staff in your ass is no fun.

{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}}
